# generate_compose.py

## Purpose
Auto-generates a production-ready `docker-compose.yml` including your application service and common sidecars (DB, cache, etc.).

## Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- `pip install ollama`
- Ollama model available locally

## Usage
```sh
chmod +x generate_compose.py
./generate_compose.py \
  --model llama3.1:8b \
  --language node \
  --env staging \
  --output docker-compose.yml


